Home-based pulmonary rehabilitation for COPD using minimal resources: An 
economic analysis.

Burge AT(1)(2)(3), Holland AE(1)(2)(3), McDonald CF(3)(4)(5), Abramson MJ(6), 
Hill CJ(2)(3), Lee AL(1)(2)(3), Cox NS(1)(3), Moore R(3), Nicolson C(1)(2), 
